

# KONSEP SINGKAT

| Komponen       | Fungsi                            |
| -------------- | --------------------------------- |
|   Postfix      | Server pengirim email (SMTP)      |
|   Dovecot      | Server penerima email (IMAP) |
|   Roundcube    | Webmail berbasis browser          |
|   User Linux   | Digunakan sebagai akun email      |

Alur kerja email:
Kirim Email → Postfix (SMTP) → Disimpan di Server → Dovecot (IMAP) → Dibaca via Roundcube

---

# SPESIFIKASI PRAKTIKUM

OS: **Ubuntu Server 20.04 / 22.04 / 24.04**
Domain: pakai **localhost** dulu (tanpa domain publik)
Akses Webmail: `http://ip-server/roundcube`
User email: user Linux (contoh: mahasiswa1)

---

# LANGKAH 1 — UPDATE SISTEM

sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y

---

# LANGKAH 2 — INSTALL POSTFIX (SMTP)

sudo apt install postfix -y

Saat muncul pilihan:

* Pilih: **Internet Site**
* System mail name: isi

  localhost

Cek apakah Postfix berjalan:

sudo systemctl status postfix

Jika aktif, berarti SMTP sudah berjalan.


# LANGKAH 3 — INSTALL DOVECOT (IMAP)

sudo apt install dovecot-imapd dovecot-pop3d -y

Aktifkan Dovecot:

sudo systemctl enable dovecot
sudo systemctl start dovecot
sudo systemctl status dovecot

Jika status active (running), maka IMAP sudah berjalan.

---

# LANGKAH 4 — KONFIGURASI DASAR DOVECOT

Edit file:

sudo nano /etc/dovecot/conf.d/10-mail.conf

Cari baris ini:

mail_location =

Ubah menjadi:

mail_location = maildir:~/Maildir

Simpan → restart Dovecot:

sudo systemctl restart dovecot

---

# LANGKAH 5 — MEMBUAT AKUN EMAIL (USER LINUX)

Setiap user Linux otomatis menjadi akun email.

Contoh buat user:

sudo adduser mahasiswa1

Masukkan password.

Artinya:

Email: mahasiswa1@localhost
Password: sesuai yang dibuat

---

# LANGKAH 6 — UJI SMTP & IMAP VIA TERMINAL

Install mail client:

sudo apt install mailutils -y

Kirim email dari user:

su - mahasiswa1
mail mahasiswa1

Ketik isi pesan → tekan:

Ctrl + D

Cek inbox:

mail

Jika pesan masuk → **SMTP & IMAP SUKSES.**

---

# LANGKAH 7 — INSTALL APACHE, PHP & DATABASE

Roundcube butuh web server dan database.

sudo apt install apache2 php php-mysql php-intl php-xml php-mbstring mariadb-server unzip wget -y

Aktifkan database:

sudo systemctl enable mariadb
sudo systemctl start mariadb

---

# LANGKAH 8 — BUAT DATABASE ROUNDCUBE

Masuk ke MariaDB:

sudo mysql

Jalankan:

CREATE DATABASE roundcube;
CREATE USER 'roundcube'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'passwordku';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON roundcube.* TO 'roundcube'@'localhost';
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;
EXIT;

---

# LANGKAH 9 — INSTALL ROUNDCUBE

cd /var/www/html
sudo wget https://github.com/roundcube/roundcubemail/releases/download/1.6.6/roundcubemail-1.6.6-complete.tar.gz
sudo tar -xvf roundcubemail-1.6.6-complete.tar.gz
sudo mv roundcubemail-1.6.6 roundcube
sudo chown -R www-data:www-data /var/www/html/roundcube

---

# LANGKAH 10 — SETUP ROUNDCUBE VIA WEB

Buka browser:

http://IP-SERVER/roundcube/installer

Isi:

* IMAP Server: `localhost`
* SMTP Server: `localhost`
* Database:

  * User: `roundcube`
  * Password: `passwordku`
  * Database: `roundcube`

Klik **Initialize Database**

Hapus installer:

sudo rm -rf /var/www/html/roundcube/installer

---

# LANGKAH 11 — AKSES WEBMAIL

Buka:

http://IP-SERVER/roundcube

Login:

Username: mahasiswa1
Password: (password linux)

Jika inbox tampil → **WEBMAIL ROUNDCUBE BERHASIL.**

---

#  OUTPUT AKHIR 

| Target               | 
| -------------------- | 
| Mail Server Lengkap  |       
| SMTP Berjalan        | 
| IMAP Berjalan        |
| Webmail Roundcube    |
| Login Email          |
| Kirim & Terima Email |

---

# RINGKASAN ALUR 

1. Install Postfix sebagai SMTP server
2. Install Dovecot sebagai IMAP server
3. Membuat akun email dari user Linux
4. Menguji pengiriman email via terminal
5. Install Apache, PHP, dan MariaDB
6. Install dan konfigurasi Roundcube
7. Login Webmail dan uji kirim-terima email

